PrecisAuthority to enter into five-year AGREEMENTS with each of the three prairie provinces (Alberta, Manitoba and Saskatchewan) and a four-year one with the Province of British Columbia which provide for the implementation of programs designed to prevent or reduce damage caused to grain crops by migrating waterfowl and for the making of financial contributions in respect thereof.
